ty, both the OIII luminosity and the\n$L[OIII]/M_{BH}$ are significantly larger in AGNs with a bright companion ($M_r\n< -20$) than otherwise.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Jan 2007 14:19:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
